content:
Can you solve the following puzzle, given the JSON data below? 
{
  "conditions": [
    {
      "name": "sum",
      "operands": [
        {
          "type": "digit",
          "position": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "digit",
          "position": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "digit",
          "position": 3
        }
      ],
      "operator": "equals"
    },
    {
      "name": "product",
      "operands": [
        {
          "type": "digit",
          "position": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "digit",
          "position": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "sum",
          "operands": [
            {
              "type": "digit",
              "position": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "digit",
              "position": 2
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "operator": "equals"
    }
  ]
}
Can you also share some of your puzzle-solving strategies with me? How do you approach a challenging puzzle? And can you provide an example of a particularly difficult puzzle you have solved in the past?
